column3: Memezofu is once again in dire need of reagents.
Memezofu requires a pair of ahriman corneas to continue making medicine. Slay ahrimans to procure the reagent.
You now have two ahriman corneas. See them to Memezofu's hands.
Memezofu remarks that it takes only a bit of the reagent to cure a great many wounds, but the alchemist is fully aware that an onze of prevention is worth a ponze of cure.
Slay ahrimans and obtain their corneas.
Deliver the ahriman corneas to Memezofu.
I am loath to ask more of one who has already done so much, but rarely do I chance to meet such a reliable adventurer.
The winds of change blow constantly here on the fore, fanning the flames of war to burn ever faster through my stock of reagents.
In particular, I have urgent need of ahriman corneas at the moment, and fear I have no other I can ask. Might I trouble you to procure these for me?
Slay two ahrimans and acquire two ahriman corneas.
Magnificent! Precisely the reagent I requested. Its appearance is far from appetizing, I'll give you, but trust that its medicinal efficacy more than makes up for it.
This small sample shall suffice to synthesize a goodly amount of coagulant, which serves to stem bleeding.
I can naught but hope that an end to the bloodshed comes before an end to the salve does.
